REZZ ANNOUNCES 8TH ANNUAL REZZ ROCKS VIII

RED ROCKS AMPHITHEATRE IN MORRISON=2C CO ON
OCTOBER 3=2C 2026

SUPPORTED BY FROST CHILDREN=2C KAVARI=2C IZZY CAMINA=2C
& SAKR

Artist Pre-Sale Begins on Thursday=2C February 26 at 10AM Local Time
General On-Sale to Follow on Friday=2C February 27 at 10AM Local Time

Register For Pre-Sale
https://laylo.com/officialrezz/RRVIII

Assets available for download here. (https://drive.google.com/drive/folder=
s/1ECpSgYpqJvZoVoSULsHgDKZUO16qCP6w?usp=3Dsharing)
February 23=2C 2026 =E2=80=94 Electronic music visionary REZZ today announ=
ces her eighth annual REZZ ROCKS VIII at Red Rocks Amphitheatre in Morriso=
n=2C CO on October 3=2C 2026. Supported by Frost Children=2C KAVARI=2C Izz=
y Camina=2C and Sakr=2C this year=E2=80=99s REZZ ROCKS will be a one-night=
 only experience.

Since its inception=2C REZZ ROCKS has evolved into one of the most anticip=
ated headline events at the legendary Colorado venue=2C serving as a platf=
orm for REZZ to fully explore the outer edges of her sound=2C visuals=2C a=
nd conceptual world-building. Red Rocks has been home to some of REZZ's gr=
eatest career milestones=2C from becoming the venue's first electronic fem=
ale headliner in 2018 to hosting its first all-female lineup in 2024. Each=
 year=2C REZZ ROCKS offers a unique chapter in her artistic evolution=2C w=
ith production=2C set design=2C and musical direction crafted exclusively=
 for Red Rocks=E2=80=99 natural amphitheater. REZZ ROCKS VIII continues th=
is tradition=2C solidifying the event as a defining moment on REZZ=E2=80=
=99s annual calendar.

Last year=E2=80=99s REZZ ROCKS VII was a two-night whirlwind spectacle=2C=
 with Night 1 featuring a surprise PORTAL set and Night 2 marking the retu=
rn of REZZs Nightmare On Rezz Street (https://youtu.be/GxHGHtcra-o?si=3Dvl=
vU5jnG0N9yeEA3) series. Together=2C the two nights captured the duality of=
 REZZ=E2=80=99s artistry=E2=80=94simultaneously forward-looking and rooted=
 in her most iconic=2C immersive experiences=2C mimicking the themes woven=
 throughout her 2025 album=2C As The Pendulum Swings (https://hypnovizion.=
lnk.tt/pendulumswings) .

REZZ ROCKS has become a celebration of REZZ=E2=80=99s creative world and h=
er fascination with horror=2C hypnosis=2C and Halloween-inspired imagery.=
 Every detail=2C from spine-chilling sonics to mesmerizing visuals=2C refl=
ects the singular aesthetic that has become a hallmark of her live perform=
ances.

The announcement comes as REZZ wraps her headline As The Pendulum Swings T=
our supporting her fifth studio album. Over the weekend=2C REZZ brought he=
r acclaimed PORTAL experience to The Armory in Minneapolis. REZZ will also=
 make her grand return to Coachella in April=2C performing on Saturday bot=
h weekends.

Artist pre-sale starts Thursday=2C February 26 with general on-sale to fol=
low on Friday=2C February 27 at 10AM Local Time. Sign up for pre-sale here=
 (https://laylo.com/officialrezz/RRVIII) .
