rld and her fascination with horror=2C hypnosis=2C and Halloween-inspired=
 imagery. Every detail=2C from spine-chilling sonics to mesmerizing visual=
s=2C reflects the singular aesthetic that has become a hallmark of her liv=
e performances.&nbsp;<br>
<br>
