gs Tour</em> supporting her fifth studio album. Over the weekend=2C REZZ b=
rought her acclaimed <em>PORTAL </em>experience to The Armory in Minneapol=
is. REZZ will also make her grand return to Coachella in April=2C performi=
ng on Saturday both weekends.&nbsp;<br>
